Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:54.89,HiguDef,,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}But to achieve that, it is necessary for everyone to unite as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ そのためには―
